'''''Dragon Magazine'' 200''' was the 200th issue and a Special Collector's Issue of [[Dragon (magazine)|''Dragon Magazine'']]. It was published by [[TSR, Inc.]] in [[December]] [[1993]].

This issue features the unlicensed ''[[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game]]'' adventure "[[The Galaxy Dragon and crew|The ''Galaxy Dragon'' and crew]]," written by [[Bill Slavicsek]] with artwork by [[Mike Vilardi]].

